snippet.title: What is the Correlation Coefficient r ?
snippet.description:
Learn how to describe correlation in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.  We discuss the correlation coefficient r as well as how to find r using the linear regression feature on the ti-83.

0:10 What is Positive Correlation, Negative Correlation or No Correlation
0:42 What Does Strong Correlation Mean and What Does Weak Correlation Mean
1:23 What Does r Represent
1:32 What Does a -1, 0, or 1 Correlation Represent
2:14 Example 1 Weak Negative Correlation 
2:43 Example 2 Positive Correlation
2:59 Example 3 Strong Positive Correlation
3:15 Example 4 Relatively No Correlation
3:43 Finding Correlation Coefficient on TI83 Using Linear Regression
6:40 How To Turn the Diagnostic On To Be Able to See r Value
